Title: Meet Me Up Top
Description:
I never thought that I would be a prisoner of the Alliance again. I cannot begin to express my gratitude to you... $n, is it?

I will meet you up top and from there we will deal with them.
ObjectivesText: Make your way up top on the upper deck of the Vengeance Wake off the shore of the Lost Isles and speak with Thrall.
RewardText: My mission is too critical to let these meddlers continue to dog us. It's up to you and I to put an end to this once and for all!
